statements: SELECT * FROM RetirementAccounts WHERE account_name LIKE 'John%'

SELECT c.account_id, c.contribution_amount, w.withdrawal_amount FROM contributions c INNER JOIN withdrawals w ON c.account_id = w.account_id ORDER BY c.date_of_contribution DESC, w.date_of_withdrawal ASC LIMIT 20;
